			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>&#8220;It&#8217;s a-me! Mario!&#8221;, right here, in your back button.</p>
<p><a href="https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/9858">Mushroom Kingdom</a>, by Matt Coxwell, brings the joyful colors of Mario&#8217;s video game adventures to your favorite browser.</p>
<p><a href="https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/9858"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2880" title="Mushroom Kingdom theme" src="http://mozillalinks.org/wp/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/mushroomkingdom.png" alt="" /></a></p>
